<h4>Ding 10!</h4>

<h3>Penalties</h3>
<p>Congratulations on another milestone. You will now lose experience when you die.
You'll also have to return to your corpse if you want to get your items back.
Magicians have a unique predicament on CR. Without the ability to root, snare or
fear a mob, we must rely on pets to control mobs. Without malachite, we cannot
make a pet. If you must fight back to your corpse, I suggest picking up some
malachite. It's a good idea to keep a few pieces in the bank for emergencies.</p>

